            <history-note id="DLM2118806"><amended-provision>Section 6(1)</amended-provision><emphasis style="bold">council organisation</emphasis> paragraph (b)(ii): <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>7 July 2004</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM303194">section 3(3)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Local Government Act 2002 Amendment Act 2004</amending-leg> (2004 No 63).</history-note>
