            <history-note id="DLM171495"><amended-provision>Section 6(4)(ca)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>inserted</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>7 July 2004</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM303194">section 3(5)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Local Government Act 2002 Amendment Act 2004</amending-leg> (2004 No 63).</history-note>
            <history-note id="DLM171494"><amended-provision>Section 6(4)(d)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>repealed</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 July 2004</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM301338">section 48(1)(b)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Local Government (Auckland) Amendment Act 2004</amending-leg> (2004 No 57).</history-note>
