              <text>Without limiting the provisions of the <citation jurisdiction="nz"><leg-title href="DLM31458">Interpretation Act 1999</leg-title></citation>, it is declared that the repeal of the Local Government (Prohibition of Liquor in Public Places) Amendment Act 2001 does not affect the amendments made to the <citation jurisdiction="nz"><leg-title href="DLM415531">Local Government Act 1974</leg-title></citation> by sections 8 and 9 of that Act.</text>
            </para>
